'''克洛伊·图顿'''（{{lang-en|Chloé Tutton}}，{{bd|1996年|7月17日||}}）生于威尔士龐特普里斯，是一名英国女子游泳运动员，主攻蛙泳<ref name=":0">{{Cite news|url=https://www.bbc.com/sport/wales/36100774|title=Rio 2016: Chloe Tutton 'shocked' by Olympic Games selection|date=2016-04-21|publisher=BBC Sport|access-date=2016-10-15|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161220123147/https://www.bbc.com/sport/wales/36100774|archivedate=2016-12-20|dead-url=no}}</ref>。她在小时候时常在节假日期间游泳，后来她的母亲将她带到当地的游泳课堂练习<ref name=":2">{{Cite news|url=http://www.walesonline.co.uk/sport/other-sport/amazing-story-rhondda-teenage-swimmer-11220563|title=The amazing story of the Rhondda teenage swimmer realising her Olympic dream|last=Griffiths|first=Gareth|date=2016-04-21|publisher=Wales Online|access-date=2016-10-15|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170619054136/http://www.walesonline.co.uk/sport/other-sport/amazing-story-rhondda-teenage-swimmer-11220563|archivedate=2017-06-19|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://results.gc2018.com/en/swimming/athlete-profile-n6027862-chloe-tutton.htm|title=Chloe Tutton|work=Gold Coast 2018|accessdate=2020-07-15|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190416030634/https://results.gc2018.com/en/swimming/athlete-profile-n6027862-chloe-tutton.htm|archivedate=2019-04-16|dead-url=no}}</ref>。12岁时，她被一位游泳教练看中，之后她移居至[[加的夫|加的夫]]，接受更深入的训练<ref name=":0" /><ref name=":2" />。16岁时，她患上[[傳染性單核白血球增多症|腺热]]疾病，不得不暂时休整<ref name=":0" />。2014年，她回归赛场，参加[[苏格兰|苏格兰]][[格拉斯哥|格拉斯哥]]举办的[[2014年英联邦运动会|英联邦运动会]]<ref name=":3">{{Cite news|url=https://www.teamgb.com/news/team-gb-exclusive-tutton-shakes-off-shock-to-follow-in-hero-davies-wake|title=Team GB Exclusive: Tutton shakes off shock to follow in hero Davies' wake|access-date=2016-10-16|date=2016-04-23|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161019020754/https://www.teamgb.com/news/team-gb-exclusive-tutton-shakes-off-shock-to-follow-in-hero-davies-wake|archivedate=2016-10-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

